{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;The world is going to end pretty soon, we've known that for some time&quot;</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Face the End</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Lenna, a teenager and avid music lover who couldn't take the silence of a decaying world anymore. Determined to bring back a bit of a spark of joy, Lenna broke into an old, abandoned radio tower, reigniting its transmitter. Your mission is to turn that silence into celebration\u2014broadcasting music, taking calls, and boosting the morale of a weary world.\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Shape the Sound</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utilize a unique music system to create your own soundtrack. Mix and match 9 different instruments per track, and manage your broadcast to the town to create the right mood for its inhabitants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426490/extras/Cable.gif?t=1739387745\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hear the Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utilize your unique position as a radio host in the tower to help the townspeople. Hear their story and use your vantage point and your trusty avian companion Tuvi to do the things that matter most in the  final days of the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426490/extras/Radio.gif?t=1739387745\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426490/extras/End_Transmission_Poster_low_res.png?t=1739387745\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>This game is the product of a six week collaboration project hosted by DADIU.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426490/extras/DADIU_White_Grayscale.png?t=1739387745\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>We would like to thank all the lovely people who made this possible - including the amazing Team Tall Trees members, the DADIU program and teachers, as well as the IT University of Copenhagen.</i></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Joyous Occasion!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3426490/5c7919aba55b76afcb068c9a883243f542a8a840.jpg"},{"name":"Resolute Radio waves","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3426490/c4798a5e7436b131c2cddec925be76c6c33332c1.jpg"},{"name":"Embraced Tranquillity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3426490/525d3d5622bf115e30e89681c7980e1c0d8f6a8b.jpg"},{"name":"I'm Ending This Transmission","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3426490/35e06759683f264eb61e76cb6d7178d151265ec4.jpg"},{"name":"Followed the Trail","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3426490/48694bf45aae969a5bc2a14b1cc684d8d84318ba.jpg"},{"name":"A Beautiful Wedding","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3426490/00d8f52af775d67988b82cc97fa64671f424f52e.jpg"},{"name":"What Does It All Mean?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3426490/759a59944c948c5ffa95dd552f600f0f459a7a8f.jpg"},{"name":"Birds and Fireflies","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3426490/d05b49fd6176e5c561907a0f58ad313dee5f0d61.jpg"},{"name":"Goodbye, Old Friend","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3426490/386fc8ea700fc39f6d8d9df23005948b668f4851.jpg"},{"name":"I Should Put on Some Music!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3426490/a121158320b99209136996a7c5cc068b1da96325.jpg"}],"total":21},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3426490?t=17